rules:
  - id: prefer-getter-agents
    description: Use lazy getters for mastra agents/mastra instance (getScraperAgent/getDesignerAgent/getMastra) instead of importing agent singletons directly.
  - id: prefer-problem-details
    description: When adding API handlers, ensure errors are wrapped into problem-details responses (via createProblemDetails) and include CORS/JSON headers.
  - id: avoid-require
    description: Avoid require(); use ES module imports.

